      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <p>
          Ella Rises was founded with a simple yet powerful vision: to create spaces where young Latinas
          can see themselves as scholars, artists, and leaders. Through culturally rooted programming,
          we help participants connect with their heritage while exploring pathways to higher education
          and meaningful careers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our programs bring together arts, music, and STEAM education to foster creativity, critical
          thinking, and confidence. We believe that when young women are given the tools and encouragement
          to rise, they transform not only their own lives but their entire communities.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, we serve over 150 girls each year through workshops, mentoring programs, and cultural
          celebrations. Our work is made possible by dedicated volunteers, generous donors, and community
          partners who share our commitment to equity and opportunity.
        </p>
      </div>
